net.dean.jraw.models

Class Captcha

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.models.Captcha

  • public final class Captcha
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Captcha (an acronym for "Completely Automated Public Turing test to tell Computers and Humans Apart"). These are required by the Reddit API for some actions that are susceptible to spam, like creating subreddits or accounts.
